{"tid":2380003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"攬鈔當歌，人生幾何？兒登水魚，冇人嫌多。","createTime":"2021-01-25T14:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T07:01:45.000Z","uid":11294,"like":94,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f95257adf80af4837525f32bde2e6c4d90473293","tid":2380003,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"《倫敦行》劉孟德<br />\n<br />\n攬鈔當歌，人生幾何？<br />\n兒登水魚，冇人嫌多。<br />\n買完跑車，戶口歸零。<br />\n何以解貧？唯有掠水。<br />\n綠綠銀子，悠悠我心。<br />\n政策倡議，鳩噏至今。<br />\n時事玩具，炒撚晒車。<br />\n我有死忠，含吹奶啜。<br />\n億億港紙，何時奪完？<br />\n錢從豬來，可一可再。<br />\n橫跨歐陸，酒店豪嘆。<br />\n狼吞虎嚥，心念丹麥。<br />\n醉漢扑頭，將計就計。<br />\n腎上腺素，毫無破綻？<br />\n錢不厭多，橋不厭舊。<br />\n劉公吹雞，天下課金。"},{"pid":"b7a1c570fa7406695bce494d0c3bc2e57b615315","tid":2380003,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c043ec2e86825293307f9605910cbcea069b0520","tid":2380003,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b5c22433f0f18ed31b97f66f48b5489e